data.title: 7 Field Commanders RK Battalion
data.meta_description: 7 Field Commanders RK Battalion - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document lists the names, ranks, and units of field commanders who were awarded the Knight's Cross. It includes over 200 entries of commanders from the army, Luftwaffe, Waffen-SS, and police units who were awarded the Knight's Cross for their leadership as a battalion commander between 1939 and 1945. The list provides brief details for each recipient such as their rank, unit designation, and date they received the award.
